    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/d9494fa5043b8257e370c7a643ddff35.webp?t=1758308879\" width=612 height=40 /></span>D-FACTOR Features innovative gameplay with a FIGHTING GAME visualization and fast-paced turn-based gameplay. Enjoy its incredible MANGA-style illustrations, finish the game with each character to discover part of their story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/03ff8cc40afe5085cf4415fd336b8fbf.poster.avif?t=1758308879\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/03ff8cc40afe5085cf4415fd336b8fbf.webm?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/03ff8cc40afe5085cf4415fd336b8fbf.mp4?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/c89a08e88b825b8ec1ee8345e40fc625.webp?t=1758308879\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select one of 12 playable characters to unlock their endings and hidden characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/b26749b2412a9bf859db6e58c074555a.poster.avif?t=1758308879\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/b26749b2412a9bf859db6e58c074555a.webm?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/b26749b2412a9bf859db6e58c074555a.mp4?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game design with MANGA style!! not comic!! SLEEVE!! to the Japanese</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful graphics</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frantic gameplay!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 characters to select!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 game modes, NORMAL or SPECIAL</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Difficulties, NORMAL or DIFFICULT</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters to unlock</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden characters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/9773c8dbde1f31cbfc9c2ffe0ace8faa.webp?t=1758308879\" width=612 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/06d10cb20dc1ba623d4bc20d99baf005.poster.avif?t=1758308879\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/06d10cb20dc1ba623d4bc20d99baf005.webm?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/06d10cb20dc1ba623d4bc20d99baf005.mp4?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/b3fc80161d81d0d8f24cf9882f578cf5.poster.avif?t=1758308879\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/b3fc80161d81d0d8f24cf9882f578cf5.webm?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/b3fc80161d81d0d8f24cf9882f578cf5.mp4?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY AND SURVIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In STORY mode, you face enemies one-on-one in turn-based combat. In SURVIVE, you must move around the map collecting cards to improve your stats; bosses are defeated in turns.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 unique ability for each character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Super attacks for each character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haruky has a transformation and a new final boss.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Mini Game Mode SURVIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive the waves of enemies to face the bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat bosses in classic mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/47f60c556e3611d8b6bc49a077811454.poster.avif?t=1758308879\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/47f60c556e3611d8b6bc49a077811454.webm?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1887360/extras/47f60c556e3611d8b6bc49a077811454.mp4?t=1758308879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
